      "content": "but wait, you said they're \"proven\" to work. isnt that a bit of a stretch? like, there's a lot of people who say that crime is actually tied to poverty or drugs rather than just how easy it is to get a gun. so how can you say it's a proven fact if people are still arguing about the actual causes?",
